title: PS3 Linux AsbestOS V1.5  on Kmeaw 3.55 CFW
description:
Description:
Kmeaw's AsbestOS Installer lets you boot a Linux kernel using LV2 Patcher v9.
Click here for more info.
AsbestOS Installer v1.3
Now auto-detects PS3 model. There is no need for two (fat and slim) pkgs.
Fixes a problem with incorrectly partitioned USB drives.
AsbestOS Installer v1.2
An ethernet cable is no longer needed (the option is still there though)
AsbestOS Installer v1.4
Improved stability
Faster LV1 scanning
AsbestOS Installer v1.5
You can now boot from network, HDD, or USB
